    <item>
      <title>०६६ विदुरकृतदुर्योधनतर्जनम्</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/mahAbhAratam/vyAsaH/goraxapura-pAThaH/hindy-anuvAdaH/02_sabhAparva/09_dyUtaparva/03_pANDavAvamAnam/066_vidurakRtaduryodhanatarjanam/</link>
